commit_message:
[FIX] Port some cleanup to admin_cleanup in scenarios

In scenarios, if we use:
@validation.required_openstack(admin=True)
we need:
@scenario.configure(context={"admin_cleanup":["xxx"]}
to clean resoureces. So we should fix some  scenarios.

Change-Id: I5c391219826b817914e0fec5038e491ccc396144
